title: Png2Ico free image converter (PNG to icon)
description:
Png2Ico GUI is graphical user interface for image conversion. This free interface supports the conversion from the PNG image type to the ICO format. 

License & download: 

License: GNU (free download, no limits)

Publisher: http://www.sunosoft.com/

Platform: Microsoft Windows 

Download: http://www.sunosoft.com/download/png2ico/png2ico.zip

Manual / screenshots: http://www.sunosoft.com/index.php?option=com_wrapper&Itemid=51

Short description:

This interface has 3 PNG2ICO conversion types:

1. Basic conversion (single PNG file is converted to the ICO file)

2. Advanced mode (all the PNG\\\&#039;s from the input folder and PNG\\\&#039;s in sub folders  are converted on a single click)

3. Server mode (all the PNG\\\&#039;s in the input folder and in sub folders are converted to icons continuously)

 

Limits:

PNG\\\&#039;s size: <256ptx256pt

Max output colors: 256

 

Png2Ico GUI is based on the command line converter \\\"png2ico\\\" by Matthias S. Benkmann.
